; Coverage for report.cc fn_quantity, fn_percent, fn_commodity
; Also covers lookup (quantity), and fn_commodity lookup

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/15 Test2
    Expenses:Food    $40.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Expenses --format "%(quantity(amount)) %(commodity(amount)) %(percent(amount, 50))\n"
10 $ 20.00%
40 $ 80.00%
end test
